Package: SArf
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Autoregressive Random Forest with Uncertainty Quantification
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kevin", "Credit", email = "kevin.credit@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Kaur", "Damanpreet", role = "aut"),
    person("Emma", "Eccles", role = "aut"))
Description: Implements spatial autoregressive random forest models with proper 
    uncertainty quantification through spatial cross-validation bootstrap. Provides
    comprehensive comparison to traditional spatial econometric models (SAR, SEM, SAC),
    variable importance with confidence intervals, ALE plots with confidence ribbons,
    and spatial diagnostics including Moran's I tests and visualization.
